---
title: Haunting Beef Strips & Oozy Cream Sauce with Mash & Veggies
description: If you feel like someone (or something) has been watching you, it may be because they are haunting your kitchen, waiting for their moment to devour these creamy beef strips. Hear their haunting hums of satisfaction when they dig into the fluffy potato mash. In fact, we're pretty sure these are actually friendly ghosts with a big appetite!
